        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
                  </div>

                <div xml:lang="gez" type="edition">
                  <note>The text below follows the manuscript
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESmy025">Gulo Maḵadā, Dabra Māʿṣo Qǝddus Yoḥannǝs, MY-025</ref>.</note>

                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Dionysius">
                    <label xml:lang="en">The story of the conversion of Dionysius the Areopagite
                    </label>
                     <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡
                      ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዲዮናስዮስ፡ ዘኮነ፡ ሰማዕተ፡ በሃገረ፡ አቴና፡ ዝንቱ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ተለዓለ፡</ab>
                     </div>

                     <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Glory">
                     <label>About the glory of the Saviour of the World</label>
                      <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ወካዕበ፡ ንነግረክሙ፡
                        ክብራቲሁ፡ ወተአምራቲሁ፡ ለክቡር፡ ወልዑል፡ እግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡
                     </ab>
                     </div>

                     <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Feasts">
                     <label>About the feasts of Saviour of the World</label>
                      <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በበስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>ወናሁ፡ ንነግረክሙ፡
                      በዓላቲሁ፡ ዓቢያን፡ ወክቡራን፡
                     </ab>
                     </div>


                     <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="ZaraBuruk">
                     <label>How Zarˀā Buruk was asked to save souls from Sheol</label>
                      <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወካዕበ፡ ንነግረክሙ፡
                      ዘከመ፡ አፍቀሮ፡ ብዙኃ፡ ለመድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ አቡነ፡ ዘርአ፡ ቡሩክ፡
                     </ab>
                     </div>


                     <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Heretics">
                     <label>Against heretics and apostates</label>
                      <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ስምዑ፡ ኵልክሙ፡ አሕዛብ፡ ወአምጽኡ፡ እለ፡ ትነብሩ፡ ውሰተ፡ ዓለም፡ በበሐውርቲሆሙ፡
                     </ab>
                     </div>

                     <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Love">
                     <label>About love to the Saviour of the World</label>
                      <ab xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>ኦአኃውየ፡ ፍቁራን፡ ውሉደ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡
                        ንዑ፡ ስምዑኒ፡ ወእነግርክሙ፡ ኵልክሙ፡ እለ፡ ታፈቅርዎ፡ ለመድኅን፡
                     </ab>
                     </div>

                </div>

        </body>
    </text></TEI>